}}'''迷路炎'''（英文：Labyrinthitis），又称'''内耳炎'''（Otitis interna），是指[[內耳|内耳]]的[[炎症|炎症]]，即内耳迷路（[[骨迷路|骨迷路]]、[[膜迷路|膜迷路]]）受到感染发炎<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Labyrinthitis and Vestibular Neuritis|url=https://www.hopkinsmedicine.org/health/conditions-and-diseases/labyrinthitis-and-vestibular-neuritis|accessdate=2021-02-28|work=|publisher=[[约翰霍普金斯大学|约翰霍普金斯大学]]|language=en}}</ref><ref name=":6">{{Cite book|chapter=Labyrinthitis|title=StatPearls|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK560506/|publisher=StatPearls Publishing|date=2021|location=Treasure Island (FL)|pmid=32809341|first=David|last=Barkwill|first2=Rubeena|last2=Arora}}</ref>。迷路炎影响内耳迷路的[[耳蜗|耳蜗]]和[[前庭系统|前庭系统]]，常由[[病毒|病毒]]感染导致，可造成长时间的[[眩暈_(醫學)|眩晕]]、[[恶心|恶心]]、[[耳鸣|耳鸣]]甚至[[听觉障碍|听觉障碍]]<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":6" /><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=迷路炎 - 症状、诊断和治疗 {{!}} BMJ Best Practice|url=https://bestpractice.bmj.com/topics/zh-cn/72|accessdate=2021-02-28|work=|publisher=[[英国医学杂志|英国医学杂志]]（BMJ）|language=zh}}</ref>。极少数情况可造成永久性听觉丧失<ref>{{Cite web|title=Labyrinthitis|url=https://www.cedars-sinai.org/health-library/articles.html|accessdate=2021-02-28|work=Cedars-Sinai|language=en-US}}</ref>。

迷路炎与'''前庭神经炎'''（英文：Vestibular neuritis；又称'''前庭神经元炎'''，Vestibular neuronitis）联系密切，有时混称，但后者实际指[[前庭神经|前庭神经]]发炎，可造成长时间眩晕而无严重听力损失<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":4">{{Cite web|title=前庭神经炎和迷路炎|url=https://www.uptodate.com/contents/zh-Hans/vestibular-neuritis-and-labyrinthitis|accessdate=2021-02-28|work=|publisher=www.uptodate.com|language=zh}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite book|chapter=Vestibular Neuronitis|title=StatPearls|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK549866/|publisher=StatPearls Publishing|date=2021|location=Treasure Island (FL)|pmid=31751056|first=Travis|last=Smith|first2=Justin|last2=Rider|first3=Steven|last3=Cen|first4=Judith|last4=Borger}}</ref>。前庭神经为[[前庭耳蜗神经|前庭耳蜗神经]]的一个分支，与人体的[[平衡觉|平衡觉]]相关<ref>{{Cite book|chapter=|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK279394/|publisher=Institute for Quality and Efficiency in Health Care (IQWiG)|date=2017-09-07|language=en|first=National Center for Biotechnology|last=Information|first2=U. S. National Library of Medicine 8600 Rockville|last2=Pike|first3=Bethesda|last3=MD|first4=20894|last4=Usa|title=How does our sense of balance work?}}</ref>。

== 致病机制 ==
迷路炎与前庭神经炎致病机制不完全明确。迷路炎可进一步分为浆液性和化脓性两类<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":3">{{Cite web|title=Labyrinthitis and Vestibular Neuritis|url=https://www.mottchildren.org/health-library/hw265594#:~:text=The%20causes%20of%20labyrinthitis%20and,after%20a%20middle%20ear%20infection.|accessdate=2021-02-28|work=|publisher=CS Mott Children's Hospital|language=en}}</ref>：

* 浆液性迷路炎即病毒性迷路炎（较常见），由内耳迷路的[[病毒|病毒]]感染所致，听力损失和眩晕的程度较化脓性为轻，听力损失通常可以恢复。
* 化脓性迷路炎即细菌性迷路炎（较少见），由[[细菌|细菌]]直接感染内耳所致，继发于[[中耳炎|中耳炎]]或[[脑膜炎|脑膜炎]]，通常表现为重度到极重度听力下降和眩晕。

此外，迷路炎与前庭神经炎的出现也可由于脑部受伤、极度压力、[[过敏|过敏]]或是药物影响。部分患者在发病前得过[[普通感冒|普通感冒]]（约30%<ref name ="inc"/>）或[[流感|流感]]<ref name=":3" />。也有[[疱疹病毒|疱疹病毒]]感染的病例<ref name=":0" />。乘飞机和[[水肺潛水|水肺潜水]]时，周围环境压力突变也可造成该病发作<ref name="pmid2317181">{{cite journal|title=Clinical aspects of inflight incapacitations in commercial aviation|date=March 1990|journal=Aviation, Space, and Environmental Medicine|issue=3|volume=61|pages=256–60|pmid=2317181|vauthors=Martin-Saint-Laurent A, Lavernhe J, Casano G, Simkoff A}}</ref><ref name="farmer">{{cite conference|editor=Farmer, Jr JC|title=Labyrinthine Dysfunction During Diving|conference=1st [[Undersea_and_Hyperbaric_Medical_Society|Undersea and Hyperbaric Medical Society]] Workshop.|volume=UHMS Publication Number WS6-15-74.|publisher=Undersea and Hyperbaric Medical Society|year=1973|pages=11|url=http://archive.rubicon-foundation.org/4291|access-date=2009-03-11}}</ref><ref name="pmid4619861">{{cite journal|title=General history of vestibular disorders in diving|author=Kennedy RS|url=http://archive.rubicon-foundation.org/2663|date=March 1974|journal=Undersea Biomedical Research|issue=1|volume=1|pages=73–81|pmid=4619861|access-date=2009-03-11}}</ref>。

该病发生率约每10万人口中有3.5例，大部分年龄为30-60岁，主要为40-50岁，但无明显性别差异<ref name ="inc"/>。

== 症状 ==
迷路炎与前庭神经炎均起病急，一次发作持续数分钟至数小时，可出现眩晕、失衡、耳鸣、耳内膨胀感/阻塞感、恶心、呕吐、视觉跳跃（由于眼部不受控运动/[[眼球震颤|眼球震颤]]）<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":6" /><ref name=":5">{{Cite web|title=Vestibular Neuronitis - Ear, Nose, and Throat Disorders|url=https://www.merckmanuals.com/home/ear,-nose,-and-throat-disorders/inner-ear-disorders/vestibular-neuronitis|accessdate=2021-02-28|work=Merck Manuals Consumer Version|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Inner Ear Infection (Labyrinthitis) Symptoms, Causes, Contagious, Treatment Cure|url=https://www.medicinenet.com/labyrinthitis_inner_ear_inflammation/article.htm|accessdate=2021-03-01|work=MedicineNet|language=en}}</ref>。迷路炎一般在几天内结束，但部分持续症状可能持续数周或数月才完全消退<ref name=":2" /><ref name=":5" />。

== 诊断 ==
依据病史，进行体格检查、听力学检查、{{link-en|眼震电图检测|Electronystagmography}}或[[核磁共振成像|核磁共振成像]]（MRI）<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":3" /><ref name=":5" />。诊断时要排除其它可导致眩晕的疾病，譬如[[良性陣發性姿勢性眩暈|良性阵发性姿势性眩晕]]、[[梅尼埃病|梅尼埃病]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Types of Vestibular Disorders|url=https://vestibular.org/article/diagnosis-treatment/types-of-vestibular-disorders/|accessdate=2021-02-28|work=VeDA|language=en-US}}</ref>。还有一些更严重的疾病与迷路炎有相同的临床特征，尤其是[[中枢神经系统|中枢神经系统]]的急性血管病变，因此必须准确区分，以避免并发症和死亡<ref name=":4" />。

== 治疗 ==
迷路炎与前庭神经炎一般可自行恢复<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":3" />。较严重的患者可服用前庭抑制剂、[[止吐药|止吐药]]或其它抑制眩晕的药物，比如[[美克洛嗪|美克洛嗪]]、[[劳拉西泮|劳拉西泮]]、Prochlorperazine等<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":5" />。由于大多数感染为病毒性，故[[抗生素|抗生素]]治疗可能无效<ref name=":3" />。

